 />\n<br />\n英國通訊管理局（Ofcom）發現中國環球電視網（CGTN）所有權結構為中國國有，違反英國法律，今天撤銷其廣播執照。<br />\n<br />\n通訊管理局表示，持有中國環球電視網在英國播放執照的星空華文傳媒（Star China Media Limited），對於中國環球電視網「並不負有編輯責任」。因此，「星空華文傳媒不符合管控執照服務的法律要求，並非合法的執照持有人」，且將執照移轉給另一個媒體集團，仍有可能與中共有瓜葛。（譯者：李佩珊/核稿：劉淑琴）1100205"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T15:09:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7066b53054345afbd1b1e6b051b85d853671ff56","tid":2395954,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"點只3個咁少<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a3dbbe64dcb61188856466f8488f8339011499d","tid":2395954,"uid":290314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T21:16:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e96749568a951a22f4f84fee5b0b3be158a34aaf","tid":2395954,"uid":254742,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T21:43:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edb525b0e6e653b2fe75f290018f6bbcfd03ce05","tid":2395954,"uid":188374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T23:22:56.000Z","msg":"中共：三個咁小笑死人咩，我當佢地condom咋，殺左佢地我都唔care呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2450662760d5837e10ecbdf5f5fd395dee5c15f1","tid":2395954,"uid":296410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-05T23:28:15.000Z","msg":"good job"},{"pid":"b4746b0116b41c2b24139f6c32979dce9198f8d4","tid":2395954,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc